      <scopecontent id="aspace_6a6ae6113a7e14e424c0694f74439140">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of prints of various Yale and New Haven, Connecticut buildings and grounds taken by Adolph Wittemann for the souvenir publication New Haven and Yale University. Included are views of Woolsey Hall, College Row, the New Haven Green, East Rock, Temple Street, and Sheffield Scientific School.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
